## Consulta usando LINQ

```csharp
app.MapGet("/inventory/by-value", (LibraryDbContext db) =>
{
    return db.Inventory
        .Include(i => i.Product)
        .GroupBy(i => i.CurrentStock >= 5
            ? "well-stocked"
            : "low")
