# Caso: Stock insuficiente

```csharp
if (!canFulfill)
{
    order.Status = Status.Backordered;

    db.FulfillmentEvents.Add(
        new FulfillmentEvent
        {
            OrderId = orderId,
            Type = "Backorder"
        });

    await db.SaveChangesAsync(ct);

    Log.Warning(
        "Orden {OrderId} enviada a Backordered.",
        orderId);

    return FulfillmentResult.Backordered;
}
```

---

# Caso: Stock suficiente

```csharp
order.Status = Status.Fulfilled;

order.CompletedUtc = DateTime.UtcNow;

db.FulfillmentEvents.Add(
    new FulfillmentEvent
    {
        OrderId = orderId,
        Type = "Fulfilled"
    });
```

Posteriormente se intenta guardar aplicando una política automática de reintentos.

